  <title>Project Structure</title>

  <para>
    Ikasan EIP adheres to the recommended Maven project structure and we
    strongly suggest that your <emphasis>Modules</emphasis> do the same. 
    If you are not familiar with Maven, then we recommend 
    <link xlink:href="http://www.sonatype.com/books/mvnref-book/reference/">Maven: The Complete Reference</link>
  </para>

  <section>
    <title>Pricing Service Directory Structure</title>

    <para>
      The project structure of the Pricing Service is as the following layout:
    </para>

    <para>
